      <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[Planning board: per-workspace Trello-style kanban with AI fill, live two-way file sync, and structured sync endpoints (.forge/board.json + board.inbox.jsonl) so agents read/mutate the board without parsing markdown. Send cards straight to agent terminals. Telegram gateway + Hermes push notifications. Vendored SwiftTerm fork with Warp-style inline path completion and reliable command-completion detection. Unified solid-surface button styling.]]></description>
